{"tid":2193808,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國曾指煽動罪違公約","createTime":"2020-09-08T06:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T06:11:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4a82b21bb25f65682e177512f06ca3e3dc17a806","tid":2193808,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T06:11:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/C6DIP7Q4UNH4NMBNV4OKTOSTCM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FC6DIP7Q4UNH4NMBNV4OKTOSTCM%2F&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqEy%2FESo4xB68IG1t9wT0pkU%3D&h=05c9c2bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FC6DIP7Q4UNH4NMBNV4OKTOSTCM%2F&h=8a15e096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/C6DIP7Q4UNH4NMBNV4OKTOSTCM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n聯合國曾指煽動罪違公約<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ae20BiVM27HO0ZXF0_YaJSl4MaI=/5826x3884/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VTMXCQ4AOVHHBJHAOQFRTALTEI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAe20BiVM27HO0ZXF0_YaJSl4MaI%3D%2F5826x3884%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVTMXCQ4AOVHHBJHAOQFRTALTEI.jpg&h=8d2df26f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳靄儀<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】煽動罪在1914年立法，屬殖民地時期用來管制新聞自由的高壓法律，內容相當過時，六七暴動後幾乎無引用過，陳文敏昨強調法律界一直認為需要修改法例。翻查資料，聯合國人權事務委員會多次關注《刑事罪行條例》煽動罪的定義太廣泛，敦促修例使其完全合乎國際公約。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩律師會指「對付批評者的武器」<br />\n<br />\n大律師吳靄儀2017年曾撰文簡述煽動罪的歷史。吳指條例自1971年以來，未曾用來檢控任何人。文章提及1996年港英政府提出《刑事罪行條例》第10(1)條時，加入「意圖導致暴力或製造擾亂公安或公眾騷亂」為須證明方可成立觸。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國人權事務委員會要求《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》締約國，須確保煽動法的法律，。。。。。"}]}